"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1150446","Ministry of Defence","false","2019-10-24","<p>As at 1 April 2019 the number of veterans receiving an Armed Forces occupational pension under the Armed Forces Pension Schemes residing in Mansfield is 916 and Nottinghamshire, as a whole, is 10,850.</p>","Plymouth, Moor View","Johnny Mercer",,"2019-10-24T14:31:08.547Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1150446/answer","Biography information for Johnny Mercer","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1150446/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1150446/answer",,,,,"11","Defence","Defence","2019-10-17","Veterans: Pensions","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Defence, how many veterans receive an armed forces occupational pension in (a) Mansfield and (b) Nottinghamshire.","false","Biography information for Ben Bradley","Mansfield","Ben Bradley","1783"
